Data Collection

This software may collect anonymous match statistics to improve the software and its features, including future predictive analytics.
No personal data is collected: player names, team names, locations or other identifying information are never transmitted; player identifiers are local to your computer and cannot be linked to real individuals by the software author.
Data collection is strictly for software improvement and analytical purposes. By using the software, you acknowledge that these anonymous statistics may be collected automatically.

